sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API
    participant ReviewModel
    participant Database

    User->>API: POST /reviews (review data)
    API->>API: Validate data (check user/place exists)
    API->>ReviewModel: Create Review object
    ReviewModel->>Database: INSERT review into DB
    Database-->>ReviewModel: Confirm insert
    ReviewModel-->>API: Return created review
    API-->>User: 201 Created + Review data